headline: Euskadi: focus of contagion
text: Spain is one of the seven countries with more than 100 cases. It has five outbreaks, two of which are extremely worrying: Torrejón de Ardoz in Madrid and Gasteiz in the Basque Country. In view of this situation, Fernando Simón, spokesman for the Ministry of Health during the pandemic, said that it was possible to eliminate classes and work in person.
